# loopfriend

loopfriend is a simple way to select and configure (looping, ideally) animations and videos as a wallpaper using [lively](https://github.com/rocksdanister/lively).

## Installation

Install the lively zip using drag-n-drop or through the import menu.

## Usage

Place your own preferred backgrounds under the backgrounds folder. You can then choose between them in the properties window.

How the background is scaled and fitted to your screen can be configured.


